CustomField.formula: IF(TEXT(Status__c) == 'Received', 1, IF( OR( TEXT(Status__c) == 'Contact Attempted', TEXT(Status__c) == 'Pre-review Passed', TEXT(Status__c) == 'Pre-review Failed', TEXT(Status__c) == 'Ready to Contact', TEXT(Status__c) == 'Contacted - Not Suitable', TEXT(Status__c) == 'Unable to Reach', TEXT(Status__c) == 'Successfully Contacted' ), 2, IF( OR(TEXT(Status__c) == 'Eligibility Passed', TEXT(Status__c) == 'Eligibility Failed' ), 3, IF( OR( TEXT(Status__c) == 'Ready to Screen', TEXT(Status__c) == 'Screening In Progress', TEXT(Status__c) == 'Screening In Progress - Wash Out Period', TEXT(Status__c) == 'Screening Failed', TEXT(Status__c) == 'Unable to Screen', TEXT(Status__c) == 'Withdrew Consent', TEXT(Status__c) == 'Eligibility Passed', TEXT(Status__c) == 'Declined Consent', TEXT(Status__c) == 'Screening Passed' ), 4, IF( OR( TEXT(Status__c) == 'Enrollment Success', TEXT(Status__c) == 'Enrollment Failed', TEXT(Status__c) == 'Withdrew Consent After Screening', TEXT(Status__c) == 'Declined Final Consent', TEXT(Status__c) == 'Randomization Failed', TEXT(Status__c) == 'Randomization Success' ), 5, 6) ) ) ) )
